General.Name: MMTsB PAO
General.Description: International Medical Center of Biomaterials Processing and Cryostorage Public Joint-stock company operates as a licensed bank for personal storage of cord blood stem cells and tissue of the umbilical cord in Russia and the CIS countries. The company was founded in 2003 and is based in Moscow, Russia. International Medical Center of Biomaterials Processing and Cryostorage Public Joint-stock company is a subsidiary of Human Stem Cells Institute PJSC.
